


                             Angular - front end technology

                                     Basic commands   
                              -------------------------

                      1.creation of angular project - ng new project-name 

                      2.To run angular project - ng serve

                      3.component creation - ng g c component-name

                      4.Service creation - ng g s service-name

                               

                               Basic concept
                           --------------------

                       1. Module - to import 3rd party library  - root Module - AppModule

                       2.componens - html, css,ts

                       3.To set up path for component - App Routing module file

                       4.routng-outlet selector (show user request html page to browser)    

                       5.Angular Services 

                       6.Dependency Injection - inside constructor
                            syntax: acces-specifier object-name:dependent-class-name

                       7. asynchronous - rxjs - observable - subscribe()    

                       8. data binding - sharing data inside a component        
                           8.1 one way binding
                             
                              8.1.1 component to view
                                   
                                   8.1.1.1 string interpulation - {{variable-name}}
                                   8.1.1.2 property binding - [attribute]="propert-name"


                             8.1.2 view to component
                              
                                 8.1.2.1 Event Binding - (event)="function-call"
                                 8.1.2.2 Event Binding using $event - (event) ="function-call($event)"
                                 8.1.2.3 Template reference variable, #variable-name

                           8.2 Two way binding

                               8.2.1 ngModel (Template Driven Forms)
                                   -import FormsModule , [(ngModel)]="variable-name" 
                                   -ngSubmit - apply it in form tag , (ngSubmit)="function call"


                        
                        9. angular directive - to manipulate DOM
                               9.1  component directive
                               9.2  structural directive - if we have to add new html element or delete an element based on condition
                                      structural directives preceeded by an *
                                      9.2.1 *ngif- add/remove html element based on condition
                                              syntax : *ngif="condition"
                                      9.2.2 *ngfor=" let variable-name of array-name"


                       10. ActivateRoute - provides acces to information about a route associated with a component

                       11. Router class  - use navigateByUrl() to navigate one page to another using ts

                       12. pipe - to convert